---
title: HelloHero: Middle Eastern Chicken Burger with Fries, Caramelised Onion & Mint Yoghurt
description: Did you say chermoula chicken, for burger night? The answer is yes and we can’t wait to take a big bite out of this Middle Eastern chicken burger, layered with mint yoghurt and caramelised onion. If you have any mint yoghurt left over, feel free to dip the fries in for some fun!
